---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="footer-content">
		<div class="footer-firm">
			<h3>Das Law</h3>
			<p>Experienced legal counsel dedicated to protecting your rights and achieving the best outcomes for you and your family.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-disclaimer">
			<p>The information on this website is for general informational purposes only. Nothing on this site should be construed as legal advice or as creating an attorney-client relationship. Every case is different, and past results do not guarantee future outcomes. Please consult with an attorney for advice regarding your individual situation.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="footer-bottom">
			<p class="copyright">&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Das Law. All rights reserved.</p>
			<p class="contact-line">123 Main Street, Suite 400, City, State 12345 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="tel:+15555555555">(555) 555-5555</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="mailto:contact@thedaslaw.com">contact@thedaslaw.com</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 2.5em 1em 1.5em;
		background: #333333;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
	}
	.footer-content {
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.footer-firm h3 {
		font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
		color: #ffffff;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
	.footer-firm p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	.footer-disclaimer {
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
		padding-top: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}
	.footer-disclaimer p {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		margin: 0;
	}
	.footer-bottom {
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
		padding-top: 1rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.copyright {
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}
	.contact-line {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		margin: 0;
	}
	.contact-line a {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.contact-line a:hover {
		color: #ffffff;
	}
</style>
